Public iOS 13.3 beta 1 released
06 Nov 2019, 21:22 by Artyom Bausov
Apple released iOS 13.3 Public beta 1.
In this update, the company fixed the RAM and added a toggle switch to disable the Memoji panel. It also increased stability and fixed minor bugs.



The firmware size is about 3.5 GB. Download iOS 13.3 Public beta 1 can now be "over the air." You only need to register with the Apple beta program.

Easy update!
